    <title type="html"><![CDATA[在github上搭建octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://ztlblog.github.io/blog/2015/06/17/git001/"/>
    <updated>2015-06-17T10:05:32+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://ztlblog.github.io/blog/2015/06/17/git001</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>搭建本地环境</h2>

<p><a href="http://www.git-scm.com/download/win">下载git</a></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>git配置 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>git config --globl user.name "ztlblog"
</span><span class='line'>git config --globl user.email "xx@163.com"
</span><span class='line'>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "xx@163.com"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><a href="http://rubyinstaller.org/downloads/">下载ruby</a></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>ruby注意事项 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>不要忘记勾选Add Ruby executables to you PATH
</span><span class='line'>将ruby的执行路径加入到环境变量中(不加可能会出现意向不到的惊喜！)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><a href="http://dl.bintray.com/oneclick/rubyinstaller/DevKit-tdm-32-4.5.2-20111229-1559-sfx.exe">下载devkit</a></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>devkit </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>解压目录中没有中文和空格
</span><span class='line'>必须先安装ruby
</span><span class='line'>cd devkit
</span><span class='line'>ruby dk.rb init
</span><span class='line'>ruby dk.rb install</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><a href="http://pan.baidu.com/s/1jGL6l3g">下载Markdown</a></p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>主要用来编写博客</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><a href="http://octopress.org/docs/setup/">octopress官网</a></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>octopress </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>git clone git://github.com/imathis/octopress.git octopress</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>修改rubygems </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>gem sources --remove https://rubygems.org
</span><span class='line'>gem sources -a http://ruby.taobao.org</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>bundle </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>gem install bundler
</span><span class='line'>bundle install</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>安装rake </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake install 
</span><span class='line'>rake generate (生成默认模版)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>创建博客及单页面 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_post['newblogName']
</span><span class='line'>rake new_page['newblogPage']</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>发布本地octopress 到github</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>假如你的用户名是username，首先新建一个命名位username.github.io
</span><span class='line'>rake setup_github_pages
</span><span class='line'>git@github.com:username/username.github.com
</span><span class='line'>rake deploy (发布到github上)</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
